# Jinja Template Snippets


**Select field with JSON schema backing**

{% set options = policy.schema.items.enum %}
<label for="roles">Allowed roles</label>
<select id="roles" name="roles" multiple>
  {% for role in options %}
    <option value="{{ role }}" {{ 'selected' if role in policy.value else '' }}>
      {{ role|capitalize }}
    </option>
  {% endfor %}
</select>
